function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)
	-- Grab Spawners and turn them on
	tArmyStart = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DGN_Kehj_FadingEcho_HoldoutGroup_ArmyStart")

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tArmyStart) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)
	-- Reactivate the monster AI
	tArmyStartActors = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DGN_Kehj_FadingEcho_HoldoutGroup_ArmyStartActors")

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tArmyStartActors) do
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idSpawner, true)
	end
	
	--Start the boss enounter
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(S_HOLDOUT_LEVEL_AREA)
	
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	-- Reactivate the monster AI
	tArmyStartActors = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DGN_Kehj_FadingEcho_HoldoutGroup_ArmyStartActors")

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tArmyStartActors) do
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idSpawner, true)
	end
	
	--Start the boss enounter
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(S_HOLDOUT_LEVEL_AREA)

	-- Grab Spawners and start turning spawners on
	tSpawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DGN_Kehj_FadingEcho_HoldoutGroup_Spawner")

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
	end
end
